# mradermacher imatrix (i1) Q4_K_M requant of the Heretic-abliterated dense
# Gemma-4-31B-it (sibling of the 26B-A4B heretic daily driver; per-variant
# refusal/KL stats not verified for 31B - check the source card). Dense 31B at
# ~18.7 GB offloads heavily on 12 GB VRAM; imatrix narrows the quality gap vs
# the Q5 tier. Ollama's built-in gemma4 RENDERER handles the chat template
# (Claude-Code-safe); confirm with the 3-system-message smoke test before
# trusting.

# --- CONTEXT CALIBRATION (Gemma 4 31B max is 262144) ---
PARAMETER num_ctx 200000
PARAMETER num_predict 65536

# --- GOOGLE/UNSLOTH RECOMMENDED GEMMA 4 PARAMETERS ---
# Verified against unsloth.ai/docs/models/gemma-4: temp 1.0, top_p 0.95, top_k 64.
PARAMETER temperature 1.0
PARAMETER top_p 0.95
PARAMETER top_k 64

# Neutral; Gemma 4 needs no repeat penalty (not specified upstream).
PARAMETER repeat_penalty 1.0

# Gemma 4 thinking: activate with <|think|> at the start of the system prompt.
SYSTEM <|think|>
